{"tid":1884580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞請公關維護高層聲譽 抹黑美斯！！！","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T02:59:54.000Z","uid":10338,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7a1d15e08d53e456e9a94a5f26d0b948c2db69","tid":1884580,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"據塞爾電台報導，西甲豪門巴塞隆拿聘請了一家公關公司，來保護貝圖美奧（Josep Bartomeu）等高層的聲譽，並且抹黑美斯（Lionel Messi）、比基以及前巴塞球員沙維（Gerard Pique）、佩奧爾（Carles Puyol）、教練哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）的形象。<br />\n     據塞爾電台消息，該公司名叫I3Ventures，該公司有數十個賬戶，但是巴塞和該公司認為這是「非官方賬戶」，這些賬戶專用於保護董事會的形象，而且還會攻擊關於巴塞的不同領域的人。　　<br />\n<br />\n　　塞爾電台還表示，巴塞在與該公司的合同中花費了近100萬歐元。該合同付款分為6部分，由不同的部門支付。巴塞承認雇傭了這些服務，但是對發表內容方面不負責，不過俱樂部要求他們發佈積極態度的信息。據巴塞消息人士表示，他們不喜歡某些發佈的內容。<br />\n<br />\n好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241b5ec56bcf6f9f399d61b32bca71c120c64a8b","tid":1884580,"uid":1354,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"活著何求係咪其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7dd6f939d73ecd8900ef2f272c585e7ba0dd84","tid":1884580,"uid":203961,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"241b5ec56bcf6f9f399d61b32bca71c120c64a8b","tid":1884580,"uid":1354,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"活著何求係咪其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"系 外判左去大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fa9b6c3af7876aa93cde87bf54dee54d1a1fc7","tid":1884580,"uid":134997,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"請我地波